的</em>开发过程比任何惊涛骇浪都更加动荡。育碧已<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/ubisoft-skull-and-bones-delay-games-canceled-202818759.html">多次推迟游戏</a>，目前计划在 2024 年 3 月底前推出，比<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/skull-bones-release-date-november-8-2022-184235615.html">计划晚了大约五年</a>。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="5844f1f7b46d44b6b2eb46f0bac5d4cf"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cUjxVKjXp5o?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p><em>骷髅会</em>看到你控制了一艘海盗船。您将能够与朋友组队，在开放世界中航行于公海，并与其他玩家一较高下，努力成为传奇海盗。当您登上越来越大的船只时，您需要让您的船员开心。希望这一切都值得等待。</p><p><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/sgf-2023"><em>在这里</em></a><em>了解夏季游戏节的所有新闻</em><em>！</em></p>本文最初出现在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/skull-and-bones-is-still-alive-will-apparently-have-a-closed-beta-in-august-175747813.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/skull-and-bones-is-still-alive-will-apparently-have-a-closed-beta-in-august-175747813.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f82fe049-3552-4b60-8401-f91507482b2e</guid><dc:creator>克里斯霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Mon, 12 Jun 2023 17:57:47 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1686592668</ingested><modified> 2023-06-12T17:57:51+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="864" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-07/cb56e6d0-fc86-11ec-b97a-e75ef648d6f2" width="1536"><media:keywords>标题</me